{"id":"e550982d-9bfb-4170-8795-b8bb2639c3f9","name":"Reimu Hakurei","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⛩️ || “Your lazy ass mistress…”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">━━━━━━⊱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 0)\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⊰━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/Jr6FXV5dvrzSTfQ88LUam.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">━━━━━━⊱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 0)\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⊰━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong><u>Sypnosis:</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You’re the shrine maiden’s servant now. I don’t know you ended up here but, at least you’re her acquaintance now. Anyways, after doing some errands and chores on her behalf, you decide to check on her, and you discover her sleeping, dreaming about money of course. She eventually wakes up, and questions why you. And afterwards suggests you should do some more chores, as if you hadn’t spent the last few hours doing exactly that.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The rest is all on you, pal.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">━━━━━━⊱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 0)\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⊰━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong><u>Notes:</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Miko!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Also nothing much to be said, just another bot I made for fun. I wasn’t really thinking about much when making this…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Also I’m interested in making scenario/RPG bots in the near future. It’s more of an afterthought but like, I’ve been slowly gaining interest for whatever reason, especially since I’m making my first multi-bot soon lmao. But only time will tell if I act upon my curiosity…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Expect a bot tmrw. Either Miku or Akyuu. Or literally any random Touhou character atp…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Anyways, enjoy! ^^</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">━━━━━━⊱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 0)\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⊰━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 161px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9sRs4fSsJ2cilJ_mRGiIl.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">━━━━━━⊱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 0)\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⊰━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong><u>Credits:</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/posts/7808767?q=kamuraaa_615+hakurei_reimu+\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">PFP</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://wall.alphacoders.com/big.php?i=656164\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Banner</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/posts/9135965?q=hakurei_reimu+white_background+\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Bad Apple Artwork</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">━━━━━━⊱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 0)\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⊰━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 118px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/u7ZZUeQieX1XrNdPQJf9N.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">━━━━━━⊱⋆⊰━━━━━━</p><p style=\"text","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"GXLoWzsWVh-YhnniykBj6.webp","creator":"Jaxland","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1446,"messages":24194,"created_at":"2025-04-24T04:13:25.105257+00:00"}